The contents of the directories:
--------------------------------

bin              -- scripts and programms to start and build the xmlBlaster

classes          -- all java-class are generated here

config           -- the configuration the xmlBlaster and ORB's

demo             -- some examples (Java,VisualBasic,Perl,C,C++,C#,Pyhton,Php).

doc              -- the xmlBlaster documentation.

lib              -- all libraries which are used by the xmlBlaster.

src              -- the core source of the xmlBlaster.

src/java         -- the core written in pure Java

src/python       -- the Python-modules for the xmlBlaster client         

src/c            -- the C files for the xmlBlaster client

src/c++          -- the C++-classes for the xmlBlaster client

testsuite        -- test cases to check the xmlBlaster features
